dod-mosa pack — content licence
================================

This pack is derived from:
    Implementing a MOSA in DoD Programs
    Office of the Under Secretary of Defense for Research and Engineering (OUSD(R&E)),
    Systems Engineering & Architecture (SE&A), February 2025
    Cleared for public release, Distribution A — DOPSR case 25-T-1210

