No source-material download link is published (see ../../docs/LICENSING.md).

This source is a work of the United States Government, prepared by OUSD(R&E), and is
therefore NOT subject to copyright protection in the United States (17 U.S.C. 105). It was
reviewed by the DoD Office of Prepublication and Security Review and cleared for public
